# 1. What is Query Optimization?
Query optimization = making SQL queries run faster & use fewer resources

Example:
-- Slow
SELECT * FROM employees;
-- Optimized
SELECT id, name FROM employees;

# 👉 Why faster?
Because it avoids unnecessary columns → less memory + faster execution
